## 3. Landing Page Templates

### Lead Generation Template
```
Header: Compelling headline with clear value prop
Subheader: Supporting benefit statement
Hero Image: Relevant, high-quality visual
CTA Button: Action-oriented, benefit-focused
Trust Signals: Testimonials, logos, badges
Form: Minimal fields, clear labels
Footer: Contact info, privacy policy
```

### Sales Page Template
```
Problem Statement: Pain point identification
Solution Introduction: How your product/service helps
Benefits Section: Key value propositions
Social Proof: Customer testimonials and case studies
Pricing: Clear, value-justified pricing
Guarantee: Risk reversal elements
CTA: Multiple conversion opportunities
```

