## 4. Case Studies

### Case Study 1: E-commerce Conversion Lift
**Client**: Online fashion retailer
**Challenge**: 2.1% conversion rate on product pages
**Solution**: 
- Simplified product images
- Added customer reviews
- Optimized add-to-cart button
**Result**: 34% increase in conversion rate

### Case Study 2: SaaS Trial Signups
**Client**: B2B software company
**Challenge**: Low trial-to-paid conversion
**Solution**:
- Streamlined onboarding process
- Added progress indicators
- Implemented exit-intent offers
**Result**: 28% increase in trial-to-paid conversion

